      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Note that this answer is correct if you use the spring-boot-starter-parent pom. In that case the &quot;start-class&quot; property is applied to the &quot;mainClass&quot; configuration parameter of the spring-boot-maven-plugin (which you can do directly if you aren&#39;t using the starter)."
