      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "One more thing to add, the parameter mentioned by @zhuguowei is also valid for the Spring Boot Maven Plugin: <code>mvn spring-boot:run -Dstart-class=com.foo.Application</code>. This is valid only if you haven&#39;t specified the mainClass in the pom&#39;s plugin"
