      "body" : "I tried to use the spring-boot-maven-plugin configuration you mentionned in my multimodules maven project, composed by several Spring boot projects and including Spring Boot as BOM dependency, and it worked like a charm. Concerning the maven-compiler-plugin, I didn&#39;t specify anything as I don&#39;t want my POM platform dependent. Maven automatically forked, so I think you can just ignore this configuration."
