    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For Kotlin with Gradle:</p>\n<pre><code>springBoot {\n  mainClass.set(&quot;com.example.MainKt&quot;)\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
